<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 12:22:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>汇丰银行完成向世博银行出售俄罗斯业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-completes-sale-russian-unit-expobank-2024-05-29/</link><description>两家银行周三表示，汇丰银行已将其俄罗斯子公司的所有权转让给世博银行，费用未公开，结束了大约两年的谈判和不确定性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:44:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-completes-sale-russian-unit-expobank-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：FDA称美国电子烟中的尼古丁类化学物质可能比尼古丁更有效</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/nicotine-like-chemicals-us-vapes-may-be-more-potent-than-nicotine-fda-says-2024-05-29/</link><description>根据美国食品和药物管理局 (FDA) 和独立机构的说法，在美国和国外推出的电子烟中使用的尼古丁替代品，例如 6-甲基尼古丁，可能比尼古丁本身更有效、更容易上瘾，尽管科学数据仍然不完整。研究人员。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/nicotine-like-chemicals-us-vapes-may-be-more-potent-than-nicotine-fda-says-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>时隔六年中日同意重启执政党会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-agree-restart-ruling-party-talks-after-six-year-hiatus-2024-05-29/</link><description>日本联合政府官员周三表示，中国和日本同意恢复执政党之间的定期会谈，这是六年来的首次。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:51:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-agree-restart-ruling-party-talks-after-six-year-hiatus-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国吉利将推出配备更省油发动机的混合动力车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-launch-hybrids-with-more-fuel-efficient-engines-2024-05-29/</link><description>中国吉利控股集团(GEELY.UL)周三表示，将于明年上半年推出一系列配备新一代更省油发动机的混合动力车型。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 09:28:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-geely-launch-hybrids-with-more-fuel-efficient-engines-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>随着电动汽车关税迫在眉睫，中国准备与欧洲达成协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-gears-up-make-deal-with-europe-ev-tariffs-loom-2024-05-29/</link><description>欧盟委员会预计将提高对中国电动汽车的关税，这将启动一轮谈判，中国高管希望此次谈判能够减轻对全球最大电动汽车行业的打击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 07:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-gears-up-make-deal-with-europe-ev-tariffs-loom-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示准备就爱沙尼亚海底电缆调查进行合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-says-ready-cooperate-estonia-subsea-cables-probe-2024-05-29/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中国随时准备与爱沙尼亚合作，对一艘中国船只进行调查，爱沙尼亚怀疑这艘船切断了爱沙尼亚的两条海底电信电缆。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 07:27:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-says-ready-cooperate-estonia-subsea-cables-probe-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>法国海外领土新喀里多尼亚解除对 TikTok 的禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ban-tiktok-lifted-french-overseas-territory-new-caledonia-2024-05-29/</link><description>法国新喀里多尼亚地区当局周三表示，法国已决定取消对海外领土新喀里多尼亚实施的 TikTok 禁令，旨在让这个遭受骚乱影响的太平洋岛屿恢复平静。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 05:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/ban-tiktok-lifted-french-overseas-territory-new-caledonia-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统称中国海警新规定“令人担忧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-says-new-china-coast-guard-rules-worrisome-2024-05-29/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，中国海警制定的新规定可能导致外国人在南海被拘留，这是事态升级，“令人担忧”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 05:24:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-president-says-new-china-coast-guard-rules-worrisome-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>市场：在亚洲，人们问，我如何避免来自美国的风险？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/market-asia-people-ask-how-do-i-derisk-america-2024-05-29/</link><description>香港的一位欧洲私人财富经理上周告诉我，他最近得到了获得台湾亿万富翁账户所需的催化剂：地缘政治。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 05:06:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/market-asia-people-ask-how-do-i-derisk-america-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>经过漫长的法律斗争后，香港民主党人准备迎接具有里程碑意义的判决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-democrats-brace-landmark-verdict-after-lengthy-legal-battle-2024-05-29/</link><description>香港高等法院本周将在一场具有里程碑意义的颠覆审判中对 16 名民主党人作出判决，批评者称这可能会对香港反对派民主运动和全球金融中心的声誉产生重大影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 04:33:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-democrats-brace-landmark-verdict-after-lengthy-legal-battle-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>罕见的口角显示中国和朝鲜在核武器问题上仍存在分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/rare-spat-shows-china-north-korea-still-odds-nuclear-weapons-2024-05-29/</link><description>韩国分析人士和官员表示，朝鲜本周对中国的罕见攻击凸显出，尽管其他领域的关系有所升温，但北京和平壤在中国非法核武器库问题上的看法并不完全一致。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 04:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/rare-spat-shows-china-north-korea-still-odds-nuclear-weapons-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲商界领袖认为中欧关系恶化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/europes-business-chiefs-see-eu-china-relations-worsening-2024-05-29/</link><description>大多数欧洲首席执行官认为，欧洲和中国之间的关系将在未来三年恶化，欧盟的去风险战略以及北京与莫斯科的密切关系被认为是最大的摩擦领域。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 04:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/europes-business-chiefs-see-eu-china-relations-worsening-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>巴布亚新几内亚领导人马拉佩称异常天气造成灾难</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-leader-marape-says-extraordinary-weather-causing-disasters-2024-05-29/</link><description>巴布亚新几内亚总理詹姆斯·马拉佩周三将这个太平洋岛国今年发生的多起灾害归咎于“异常降雨”和天气模式的变化，其中包括上周可能造成数千人死亡的山体滑坡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 03:21:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/papua-new-guinea-leader-marape-says-extraordinary-weather-causing-disasters-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>随着降息疑虑重新浮现，债券收益率飙升，股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-29/</link><description>由于数据引发了人们对美联储降息时机和幅度的新疑虑，美国政府债券收益率周三升至近四周高位，提振了全球债券收益率并给股市带来压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-29/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报道称，军演结束后不到一周，中国又恢复了军事活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-drills-more-about-intimidation-propaganda-than-starting-war-2024-05-29/</link><description>周三，台湾报道中国在附近重新进行军事活动，称中国军舰和战机正在进行“联合战备巡逻”，距离北京结束为期两天的军演不到一周。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 02:12:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-drills-more-about-intimidation-propaganda-than-starting-war-2024-05-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>